### Get all tasks
GET {{BASE_URL}}/tasks

### Get a single task by ID
GET {{BASE_URL}}/tasks/1

### Create a new task
POST {{BASE_URL}}/tasks
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "New Task",
  "description": "Description for new task",
  "dueDate": "2025-12-31"
}

### Update a task by ID
PUT {{BASE_URL}}/tasks/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Updated Task Title"
}

### Delete a task by ID
DELETE {{BASE_URL}}/tasks/1
